[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par Black just played the one-space jump at \'a1\'e3. Black played here to live, but actually it is the opposite.
\par
\par Find the move which captures Black. Also think about what was the correct move for Black.
\par
\par
\par }
