Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's\cf1\b  cut\cf0\b0  at 1 is the \cf1\b starting point\cf0\b0 .
\par After White plays here, Black is in trouble.
\par
\par After Black 2, White plays at 3 (or at A) and the eye becomes false on this side, so Black is dead.
\par }
