Dia. 03 Captured?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's attach at 1 is a \cf1\b mistake\cf0\b0 .
\par However Black 2 is another one.
\par
\par White throws-in at 3 and it is possible to capture Black.
\par If Black plays at 3 instead of 2, he is alive.
\par }
