Dia. 04 Black's Correct Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par From the beginning Black's diagonal move at 1 is the \cf1\b correct move\cf0\b0  then Black can live.
\par
\par After White 2, Black 3 is another \cf1\b great move\cf0\b0 . Black has to sacrifice his three stones, but he can live up to 5.
\par
\par
\par }
